statements: SELECT * FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE route_id = 1;
SELECT origin, destination, distance FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE distance > 100;
SELECT destination, origin FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE delivery_time > '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT route_id, destination FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE origin = 'City A';
SELECT * FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE distance BETWEEN 50 AND 150;
SELECT * FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE route_id = 1 ORDER BY destination DESC;
SELECT origin, destination FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE distance > 100 ORDER BY delivery_time ASC;
SELECT route_id, origin, destination, distance FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE origin LIKE '%City%' AND distance < 200 ORDER BY route_id;
SELECT route_id, destination, distance, delivery_time FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE destination = 'City A' OR destination = 'City B' ORDER BY delivery_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM DeliveryRoutes WHERE delivery_time >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY route_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM delivery_routes
SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location FROM delivery_routes
SELECT route_id, distance FROM delivery_routes WHERE distance > 50
SELECT start_location, end_location, delivery_time FROM delivery_routes ORDER BY delivery_time DESC
SELECT history_id, route_id, analyzed_date FROM route_history
SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location, distance, delivery_time FROM delivery_routes WHERE distance > 100 ORDER BY delivery_time DESC

SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location, distance, delivery_time FROM delivery_routes INNER JOIN route_history ON delivery_routes.route_id = route_history.route_id WHERE analyzed_date >= '2022-01-01'
SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location, AVG(distance) AS avg_distance FROM delivery_routes GROUP BY route_id HAVING avg_distance > 50 ORDER BY route_id
SELECT MAX(average_delivery_time) AS max_delivery_time, MIN(average_delivery_time) AS min_delivery_time FROM route_history
SELECT start_location, end_location, distance FROM delivery_routes WHERE start_location LIKE 'New%' OR end_location LIKE '%City%' ORDER BY start_location ASC, end_location DESC
SELECT * FROM delivery_routes;
SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location FROM delivery_routes ORDER BY route_date ASC;
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_date, delivery_time FROM delivery_history WHERE delivery_status = 'delivered';
SELECT driver_id, total_deliveries, rating FROM driver_performance ORDER BY total_deliveries DESC;
SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location, driver_id FROM delivery_routes WHERE route_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM delivery_routes LIMIT 10;
SELECT driver_id, start_location, end_location FROM delivery_routes WHERE route_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT delivery_id, delivery_date, delivery_time, delivery_status FROM delivery_history ORDER BY delivery_date DESC, delivery_time DESC;
SELECT driver_id, total_deliveries, missed_deliveries, avg_delivery_time FROM driver_performance WHERE rating > 4.5 ORDER BY total_deliveries DESC;
SELECT route_id, driver_id, route_date, start_location, end_location, dp.rating FROM delivery_routes dr JOIN driver_performance dp ON dr.driver_id = dp.driver_id WHERE dp.rating >= 4.0;

SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location FROM delivery_routes WHERE distance_km > 10;
SELECT * FROM delivery_orders WHERE delivery_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY delivery_date DESC;
SELECT agent_name, phone_number FROM delivery_agents WHERE agent_id = 5;
SELECT route_id, COUNT(*) as total_orders FROM delivery_orders GROUP BY route_id;
SELECT * FROM delivery_routes;
SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location FROM delivery_routes WHERE distance > 100;
SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location, distance FROM delivery_routes ORDER BY distance DESC;
SELECT agent_name, agent_email FROM delivery_agents WHERE agent_phone LIKE '%123%';
SELECT route_id, cost FROM delivery_costs WHERE vehicle_id = 1 AND cost < 50;
SELECT * FROM delivery_routes WHERE distance > 100 ORDER BY time_taken DESC;
SELECT route_id, start_location, end_location, distance FROM delivery_routes WHERE time_taken < 60 AND end_location = 'Warehouse' ORDER BY distance ASC;
SELECT d.route_id, d.start_location, d.end_location, h.date FROM delivery_routes d JOIN delivery_history h ON d.route_id = h.route_id WHERE h.delivery_status = 'Delivered' ORDER BY h.date DESC;

SELECT v.vehicle_id, v.vehicle_type, v.max_capacity, v.current_load, c.cost FROM delivery_vehicles v JOIN delivery_costs c ON v.vehicle_id = c.vehicle_id WHERE c.cost < 500 ORDER BY v.max_capacity DESC;
SELECT a.agent_id, a.agent_name, a.agent_email, c.cost FROM delivery_agents a JOIN delivery_costs c ON a.agent_id = c.route_id WHERE c.cost > 100 ORDER BY a.agent_name ASC;
